  * Simple Gemini image CLI wrapper (no dependencies).
  *
  * Usage:
  *   nanobanana --prompt "A banana astronaut in space"
  *   nanobanana -p "Stylize this" -i .\ref1.png -i .\ref2.jpg --resolution 512
